## Contributing

Want to contribute?

- See [`CONTRIBUTING.md`](CONTRIBUTING.md) for how to add new converters
- Keep things modular â€” one class per source/target, grouped by format type
- Follow naming conventions and interface expectations
- PRs are welcome!

